        "a11yReviewed": false,
        "notes": "Icon-only action — back chevrons, close (×), more-options (⋮), toolbar utilities. Renders .btn-icon (44px neutral, default) or .btn-icon-primary (32px teal). Required ariaLabel prop becomes the aria-label; the inner <i> is aria-hidden. Anchor when href provided; button otherwise. asComponent prop accepts a caller-supplied component (router-Link) so SPA navigation does not require leaking router APIs into the design system; linkProps spreads onto it. Not a terminal action — does not satisfy the wireframe-completeness gate."
      }
